reagent-name-lemintrozine = Lemintrazine
reagent-desc-lemintrozine = A sedative and a VERY strong painkiller chemical.

reagent-name-universal-blood = Universal Blood Replacement
reagent-desc-universal-blood = Created by Nanotrasen's advanced medical science, works on most races except those based on Ammonia due to complex biological incompatibilities. If given to incompatible races, rapidly induces a fatal heart attack.

reagent-name-necrosol = necrosol
reagent-desc-necrosol = A necrotic substance that seems to be able to heal frozen corpses. It can treat and rejuvenate plants when applied in small doses.
